{"tid":2118161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【7.21一年】《蘋果》獲內部通訊 證指揮官令警員「死守」元朗警署 勿理999報案","createTime":"2020-07-21T09:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T11:51:03.000Z","uid":75778,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"66de3b7b4ebd252c9708eae4f31de27a58ed3e71","tid":2118161,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:48:53.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》近日接獲聲稱屬警方內部「案件管理及調查系統（CMIS）」的案件通訊紀錄，提到元朗警區行動室（DOR YLDIST）曾作通知，稱元朗區指揮官（DC YLDIST）已指示所有人員（ALL MAN POWER）在元朗警署戒備。該紀錄更表示，警方（POLICE）不會處理任何999報案的案件。所述情況與片段中大批警員「死守」元朗警署脗合。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》上周就有關指令內容向警方查詢。警方上周五回應指，當晚絕無要求元朗警區人員怠慢處理任何市民的報案，又指該匿名指控純屬惡意捏造，用以抹黑警隊，煽動仇恨，對此深表遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">《蘋果》隨後原句引述該CMIS紀錄，再向警方查詢。警方周一終承認，元朗警署及天水圍警署於7.21當晚，門外有多人「叫囂」及「包圍警署」。元朗警區臨時指揮中心接報後，指示其他巡邏人員，在完成手頭上的工作後，立刻返回警署候命，預備展開警署防衞。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nsource by apple<br />\n【7.21一年】《蘋果》獲內部通訊 證指揮官令警員「死守」元朗警署 勿理999報案<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200721/US2VORAJ4RJJXPJMFXEYXZUZME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FUS2VORAJ4RJJXPJMFXEYXZUZME%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=879a72b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FUS2VORAJ4RJJXPJMFXEYXZUZME%2F&h=972cf874\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200721/US2VORAJ4RJJXPJMFXEYXZUZME/</a>"},{"pid":"b58f77d2ef10523def56cf885d27d1b007c8f5d1","tid":2118161,"uid":10905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"牙膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c0b6bccb2c68d30157f8f7aaa63c85b791c6a6","tid":2118161,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07